text: Guénhaël Huet (born 30 July 1956) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Manche department, and is a member of the Republicans. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:The Republicans (France) politicians Category:People from Manche Category:Mayors of places in Normandy Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Panthéon-Assas University alumni
